    "This metadata helps to filter and prioritize the retrieved information.3.",
    "Embedding Generation: Each text segment is transformed into a dense vector representation using a specialized medical embedding model, E5-large-v2 [3], which has shown superior performance in the capture of clinical semantic relationships.",
    "4.Vector Database Indexing: The generated embeddings, along with their corresponding source text and metadata, are stored and indexed in a vector database (e.g., Pinecone) optimized for efficient similarity search operations.",
